! CodeMirror 6

A modern text editor for TiddlyWiki based on [ext[CodeMirror 6|https://codemirror.net/]].

!! Built-in Features

* ''Syntax Highlighting'' — TiddlyWiki wikitext with nested language support
* ''Autocompletion'' — tiddler titles, macros, widgets, variables, filters
* ''Multiple Cursors'' — edit multiple locations simultaneously (Ctrl+Alt+Up/Down)
* ''Search & Replace'' — regex support, case sensitivity, whole word matching
* ''Bracket Matching'' — highlight matching brackets and auto-close
* ''Undo/Redo'' — unlimited history
* ''Focus Navigation'' — Ctrl+. / Ctrl+Shift+. to move between fields
* ''Spellcheck'' — browser spellcheck integration (optional)

!! Configuration

Configure via ''Control Panel → Settings → CodeMirror'':

* ''Editor'' — line wrapping, bracket matching, indentation, spellcheck
* ''Theme'' — color scheme with auto palette matching
* ''Keymap'' — VSCode (default), vim, or emacs bindings
* ''Keyboard Shortcuts'' — customize all shortcuts

