Additional language plugins are available for Python, Java, C/C++, Rust, Go, SQL, LaTeX, Sass, Lezer, PHP, and WAST.

!! Theme Plugins

Color schemes: Ayu, Catppuccin, Dracula, Everforest, Flexoki, GitHub, Gruvbox, Kanagawa, Material, Monokai, Nord, One, Palenight, Rose Pine, Solarized, Tokyo Night, Zenburn

Most themes include both light and dark variants.

!! Keyboard Shortcuts

|!Shortcut |!Action |
|Ctrl+Z |Undo |
|Ctrl+Y |Redo |
|Ctrl+F |Find |
|Ctrl+H |Find and Replace |
|Ctrl+D |Select next occurrence |
|Ctrl+/ |Toggle comment |
|Ctrl+Alt+Up/Down |Add cursor above/below |
|Ctrl+. |Focus next field |
|Ctrl+Shift+. |Focus previous field |
|Alt+Up/Down |Move line up/down |
|Tab |Indent / accept completion |
|Ctrl+Space |Trigger completion |

Customize shortcuts in ''Control Panel → Settings → CodeMirror → Keyboard Shortcuts''.

All features can be individually enabled/disabled via ''Control Panel → Settings → CodeMirror''.
